{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-hub-js","path":"/silver-spring","result":{"data":{"defaultLogo":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/6d161/sunrise-logo-padded.png","srcSet":"/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/94657/sunrise-logo-padded.png 38w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/5db04/sunrise-logo-padded.png 75w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/6d161/sunrise-logo-padded.png 150w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/7e7e9/sunrise-logo-padded.png 225w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/f006c/sunrise-logo-padded.png 246w","sizes":"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px"}}},"defaultHero":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5859030837004404,"src":"/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/7f945/default-hero.jpg","srcSet":"/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/e2788/default-hero.jpg 360w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/7d509/default-hero.jpg 720w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/7f945/default-hero.jpg 1440w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/47dad/default-hero.jpg 2160w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/af56c/default-hero.jpg 2880w","sizes":"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px"}}},"events":{"nodes":[]},"hub":{"name":"Silver Spring","about":"<p>Hello! We are Sunrise Movement Silver Spring (a.k.a. \"Sunrise Silver Spring\"), the Silver Spring, MD hub of the Sunrise Movement!</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400;\">We are currently working alongside other community groups and supportive councilmembers to pass the HOME Act (Bill 16-23, learn more <a href=\"https://twitter.com/KristinMink_/status/1633978118347137024\">here on Councilmember Mink's page</a>), which would </span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><strong>limit </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><strong>rent increases to&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><strong>3% per year&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400;\">in our county while still guaranteeing a fair return for property owners. The HOME Act is great, because it would prevent black, brown and working class community members from being displaced by big rent increases! This is especially important as opponents of rent stabilization are introducing a competing bill (the so-called \"Anti-Rent Gouging\" bill) which would allow landlords to charge higher rents than ever before, and therefore would displace a lot of community members. You can see a comparison of the two bills <a href=\"https://twitter.com/KristinMink_/status/1633978118347137024\">here</a>.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400;\">This is the biggest issue in our county and it intersects with many climate and housing justice issues. We cannot stand by idly as working class people and people of color, including our own members, friends, and family, are priced out of their homes by exorbitant rent increases. We also cannot expand rapid transit or build green housing until we can ensure that everyone here will be able to afford it. So, let's make this county affordable and sustainable for everyone by passing the HOME Act!</span><br></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400;\">If you're interested in joining our group or learning more about us, please email <a href=\"mailto:sunrisesilverspring@gmail.com\">sunrisesilverspring@gmail.com</a> and we will be happy to share our meeting details and more :) you can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SunriseMvmtSS\">Twitter</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sunrisemvmtss/\">Instagram</a>&nbsp;@SunriseMvmtSS to stay up to date on our coalition's rent stabilization campaign. Let's do this!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"twitter-timeline twitter-timeline-rendered\" style=\"display: flex; width: 500px; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-1\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center; position: static; visibility: visible; width: 500px; height: 500px; display: block; flex-grow: 1;\" title=\"Twitter Timeline\" src=\"https://syndication.twitter.com/srv/timeline-profile/screen-name/SunriseMvmtSS?dnt=false&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-1&amp;%3D&amp;frame=false&amp;hideBorder=false&amp;hideFooter=false&amp;hideHeader=false&amp;hideScrollBar=false&amp;lang=en&amp;maxHeight=500px&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fsunrise-hubhub.herokuapp.com%2Fmicrosite%2Fedit&amp;sessionId=eb6d80f41f50890cd0e88e5ab4a6940f92e42cbe&amp;showHeader=true&amp;showReplies=false&amp;theme=light&amp;transparent=false&amp;widgetsVersion=aaf4084522e3a%3A1674595607486\"></iframe></p> <script async=\"\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>","email":"sunrisesilverspring@gmail.com","website":null,"twitter":"https://twitter.com/SunriseMvmtSS","facebook":null,"instagram":"https://instagram.com/SunriseMvmtSS","signup":null,"donations":null,"websiteText":null,"logo":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/d47b2ba38486c42c7ae7dc29dac1a4be/aabdf/logo_1599766783.jpg.jpg","srcSet":"/static/d47b2ba38486c42c7ae7dc29dac1a4be/4ec6b/logo_1599766783.jpg.jpg 38w,\n/static/d47b2ba38486c42c7ae7dc29dac1a4be/25b50/logo_1599766783.jpg.jpg 75w,\n/static/d47b2ba38486c42c7ae7dc29dac1a4be/aabdf/logo_1599766783.jpg.jpg 150w,\n/static/d47b2ba38486c42c7ae7dc29dac1a4be/07ab6/logo_1599766783.jpg.jpg 225w,\n/static/d47b2ba38486c42c7ae7dc29dac1a4be/9dc27/logo_1599766783.jpg.jpg 300w,\n/static/d47b2ba38486c42c7ae7dc29dac1a4be/6ed45/logo_1599766783.jpg.jpg 2100w","sizes":"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px"}}},"hero":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3333333333333333,"src":"/static/fb8fe457072c9df5a294c22fc012ae3f/10d63/hero_1678508272.jpg.jpg","srcSet":"/static/fb8fe457072c9df5a294c22fc012ae3f/e2788/hero_1678508272.jpg.jpg 360w,\n/static/fb8fe457072c9df5a294c22fc012ae3f/7d509/hero_1678508272.jpg.jpg 720w,\n/static/fb8fe457072c9df5a294c22fc012ae3f/10d63/hero_1678508272.jpg.jpg 1080w","sizes":"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px"}}},"documents":[]}},"pageContext":{"id":"b0b9aef2-9be2-5dd9-b187-cbbe02e7a1ca"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1219170061","3649515864"]}